column2: SELECT s.plate, s.fiberid, s.mjd, s.ra, s.dec, el.sigmaStars, el.sigmaStarsErr, el.Sigma_Hb_#, el.Sigma_Hb_#_Err, el.Sigma_OIII_#, el.Sigma_OIII_#_Err, fs.logMass, fs.logMass_median, fs.tau, fs.tau_mean, ws.w1mpro, ws.w1sigmpro, ws.w2mpro, ws.w2sigmpro, ws.w3mpro, ws.w3sigmpro, ws.w4mpro, ws.w4sigmpro from SpecObj as s into mydb.joshi_xrg_match_catalog JOIN photoobjall as ph on s.bestObjID = ph.objID JOIN mydb.Joshi_XRG as ch on s.plate = j.plate and s.mjd = j.mjd and s.fiberid = j.fiberid JOIN emissionLinesPort as el on s.plate = el.plate and s.mjd = el.mjd and s.fiberid = el.fiberid JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranWideDust as fs on s.plate = fs.plate and s.mjd = fs.mjd and s.fiberid = fs.fiberid JOIN wISE_xmatch as wg on s.bestObjID = wg.sdss_objid JOIN wISE_allsky as ws on ws.cntr = wg.wise_cntr
